title: 31: The Champion's Mindset with Olympian Dr. Jeff Spencer
description:
A champion's mindset is essential for massive success in business and in life. In this episode my friend Dr. Jeff Spencer and I break down exactly how you can apply simple tactics to manifest a champion's mindset.
